Options:|Functionalities:
-install <package>|Install a package including its required dependencies
<package>|Display package information and prompt user for installation
-install --version <package>|Install specified version of the package for backward compatibility
-install --compile <package>|Install a package by fetching source code and manually compiling it
-update|Fetch the most current listing of packages available
-upgrade|Upgrade every installed package and dependencies to most recent version
-list|List all packages available for installation
-remove <package>|Delete specified package and orphaned packages
-remove --cleanup|Delete orphaned packages or obsolete dependencies to optimize disk space
